<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description"
        content="NeuroCare AI - Early Detection of Alzheimer's Risk using XGBoost Machine Learning. Responsive screening tools for cognitive health.">
    <title>NeuroCare AI - Early Alzheimer's Detection</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-body-bg text-primary-dark font-outfit antialiased">

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="glass-nav fixed top-0 left-0 w-full py-3.5 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a class="font-extrabold text-xl text-primary-blue flex items-center gap-2" href="/">
                <i class="bi bi-activity text-secondary-blue text-2xl"></i> NeuroCare AI
            </a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6">
                <a class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-dark border-b-2 border-secondary-blue pb-0.5 transition-all"
                    href="/">Home</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-secondary-blue transition-all"
                    href="/predict">Prediction</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-secondary-blue transition-all"
                    href="#about">About</a>
                <a class="btn-primary-gradient px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm" href="/predict">Start Prediction</a>
            </div>
            <div class="md:hidden">
                <a class="btn-primary-gradient px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs" href="/predict">Start Screening</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
        class="relative pt-28 pb-16 overflow-hidden bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_20%,rgba(224,242,254,0.6)_0%,rgba(248,250,252,0)_50%)]">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16">
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-left animate-fade-in">
                    <span
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-[11px] font-bold px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-5 uppercase tracking-wider">
                        <i class="bi bi-cpu-fill"></i> Powered by XGBoost ML
                    </span>
                    <h1
                        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.75rem] font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.2] mb-5">
                        Early Detection of Alzheimer Risk Using Artificial Intelligence
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-base leading-relaxed mb-7 max-w-lg">
                        Analyze clinical, behavioral, and cognitive parameters to estimate early-stage Alzheimer's risk
                        using advanced machine learning models.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                        <a href="/predict"
                            class="btn-primary-gradient py-3 px-6 rounded-xl text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-shield-plus"></i>Start Screening
                        </a>
                        <a href="#features" class="btn-outline-custom py-2.5 px-6 rounded-xl text-sm">
                            Learn More
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div
                        class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-medium border border-white/80 animate-float max-w-[420px]">
                        <img src="/images/hero_illustration.png" alt="Brain Technology Medical AI"
                            class="w-full h-auto object-cover">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section id="features" class="py-16 bg-slate-50/80">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
            <div class="text-center mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                <span class="text-secondary-blue font-bold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest">Features</span>
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold mt-2.5 text-slate-900">Advanced Features for Alzheimer
                    Prediction</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">A comprehensive, data-driven framework built to
                    understand cognitive health risk profiles.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-7 rounded-2xl flex flex-col items-start text-left">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">
                        <i class="bi bi-robot"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">AI Prediction</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Employs an optimized XGBoost classifier model evaluating multidimensional medical data to output
                        clear probability ratings.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-card p-7 rounded-2xl flex flex-col items-start text-left">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">
                        <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">Fast Screening</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Complete our simplified 18-parameter form in under 3 minutes, producing instant and clear
                        diagnostic risk summaries.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-card p-7 rounded-2xl flex flex-col items-start text-left">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-secondary-blue flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">
                        <i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line-fill"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">Importance Analysis</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Highlights primary risk drivers like cognitive scores (MMSE), functional skills (ADL), and sleep
                        quality indicators.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Statistics Section -->
    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
            <div class="bg-slate-950 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute -top-1/2 -right-1/4 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 blur-[80px]"></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
                    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 text-left">
                        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold mb-2">Model Accuracy</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Our model is validated against clinical databases using strict stratification matrices.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 md:gap-4">
                        <div class="text-center py-5 px-3 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/60">
                            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-sky-400">95.4%</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1.5 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">
                                Accuracy</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center py-5 px-3 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/60">
                            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-sky-400">94.8%</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1.5 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">
                                Precision</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center py-5 px-3 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/60">
                            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-sky-400">93.9%</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1.5 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">Recall
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center py-5 px-3 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/60">
                            <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-sky-400">94.3%</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] mt-1.5 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">
                                F1-Score</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="py-16 bg-slate-50/50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-start">
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-left">
                    <span class="text-secondary-blue font-bold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest">About</span>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-2.5 mb-5">NeuroCare AI Screening
                        Tool</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Alzheimer's disease is a progressive neurodegenerative disorder that accounts for 60-80% of
                        dementia cases. Early detection provides patients and families with a crucial timeline to adjust
                        lifestyle habits, coordinate clinical support, and access treatments that can delay cognitive
                        decline.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        NeuroCare AI bridges the gap between machine learning and healthcare. By evaluating
                        demographics, lifestyle patterns, cardiovascular metrics, and cognitive assessments, our tool
                        highlights potential risk signals before symptoms escalate.
                    </p>

                    <div class="border-l-4 border-secondary-blue bg-sky-50/70 p-5 rounded-r-xl">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm mb-1.5">
                            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill text-secondary-blue text-sm"></i> Medical
                            Disclaimer
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">
                            This screening system is powered by standard machine learning models intended for
                            educational and early screening reference. It is NOT a replacement for professional medical
                            diagnosis.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-3">
                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden" open>
                        <summary
                            class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            Why XGBoost Algorithm?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            XGBoost (Extreme Gradient Boosting) is a powerful tree-boosting algorithm renowned for
                            handling tabular medical datasets. It manages correlation across clinical variables, handles
                            outliers effectively, and produces highly interpretable results for feature importance.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                        <summary
                            class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            What are the 18 evaluated parameters?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            The model evaluates: Age, Gender, BMI, Physical Activity, Sleep Quality, Diet Quality,
                            Smoking, Alcohol, Diabetes, Hypertension, Cardiovascular Disease, Depression, Head Injury,
                            Family History of Alzheimer's, MMSE score, ADL score, Functional Assessments, and subjective
                            Memory Complaints.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                        <summary
                            class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-sm text-slate-900 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            How is risk score calculated?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400">
                                <svg fill="none" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20">
                                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-5 pb-5 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            The risk scoring calculates a probability indicator using a weighted model matrix based on
                            feature importance findings. Parameters like low MMSE, poor ADL, genetic family history, and
                            poor lifestyle habits accumulate risk scores.
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-400 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 text-left mb-10">
                <div>
                    <a class="font-extrabold text-xl text-white flex items-center gap-2 mb-3" href="/">
                        <i class="bi bi-activity text-sky-400"></i> NeuroCare AI
